processors-challenge-snapdragon-888\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.androidcentral.com/mediatek-unveils-flagship-dimensity-1100-1200-5g-processors-challenge-snapdragon-888\"\u003eDimensity 1100\u003c/a\u003e, two chips that are very familiar within the Retroid community. These will be paired with 8GB of RAM and 128GB of expandable storage to go along with a 5,000mAh battery.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-imageGallery-CyYsNJQ3RnViVLZ62qjugh-okSBiu1AXl08AAzDCWKtmXJqBWkkX2Dc\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage 1 of 2\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv aria-hidden=\"false\" data-swipeable=\"true\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture data-hydrate=\"true\"\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/cyclingnews/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K.jpg\" data-pin-nopin=\"true\" data-slice-image=\"true\"/\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5BdfwnrA3dwMCWotaE3K-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nc5